Joel 2:17
Inter vestíbulum et altáre plorábunt sacerdótes, minístri Dómini, et dicent: Parce, Dómine, parce pópulo tuo: et ne des hereditátem tuam in oppróbrium, ut dominéntur eis natiónes.
Between the porch and the altar the priests, the ministers of the Lord, shall weep, and shall say: Spare, O Lord, spare thy people; and give not thy inheritance to reproach, that the heathen should rule over them.
